Sharing food is the best ways to create memories ✨
•
Are you craving some hearty Malay-Indo food? Why not check out @dancingfish.sg! Using only the freshest and finest ingredients, they aim to bring you enjoyable and extensive flavours without adding MSG and preservatives. Their limited menu features a selection of Individual Sets, Signature Sets (for 2 pax), and some specials. Our favourite was the Cumi-Cumi Bakar Set and Chicken Satay! 🤤🤤
•
Available for delivery & self pick up with up to 30% off their delivery menu.
•
✨Free delivery with minimum spend of $60
✨$15 delivery fee for orders below $60
•
Call 63391048 to place your order!
